Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Saitama City"\N"City of Roses"\N"Chuo Ward"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Bonus Lv. 1:\N'Most strange spell names\Nhave unknown origins'"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sparklers"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll be all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I'm {\i0}gonna go out with a {\i1}bang{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ooh! Niiice!\N--Hey! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of that fireworks show\Nin our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, last year in Konosu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's when you and Tama first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,First...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Mimimi hadn't talked much at all\Nby the summer of our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Not at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're wearing your\Nwinter uniform already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I know it's still a little hot today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but this blazer is just so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just make the\Nswitch tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's switch to blazers tomorrow!\N--What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl in your class\Nwho's kind of a loner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure she {\i1}wants{\i0}\Nto be friends with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then try talking to her\Na little bit every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what, Natsubayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute--like a tiny little animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Poke, poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd {\i1}this {\i0}come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This? Oh... nowhere special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Hanabi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you again! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, all your protests\Nreally get me going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your endgame here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just go around smelling people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hit the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat together in the caf!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now, hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All that sexual harassment\Nmust really suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimimi doesn't know when to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you big meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, {\i1}super {\i0}blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aoi Hinami, from first-year class 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the Hanabi Natsubayashi\Nthat Mimimi's been bugging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So Minmi's been doing this\Nall along to help me fit in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But keep this conversation\Nbetween us, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I haven't thanked Minmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her keep up her front, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Sounds like it was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Si! {\i0}Thanks, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, Aoi:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the off-season\Nfireworks show this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Konosu Fireworks Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Si! {\i0}Nice, Aoi--you're a sharp one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about going myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they firing off some Guinness\NWorld Record-breaking shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We can go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda wanted to ask Hanabi to come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the girl whose face\Nyou've been in every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... are you sure?\NI'm in a different class and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, your advice helped me\Nand Hanabi become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you two to be friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love for you to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it. Then yes--introduce us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A fireworks show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you might not be a fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's this friend\NI want to you to meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We do track-and-field together:\NAoi Hinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoi Hinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's another ultra-cutie pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What an easy yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me {\i1}you're{\i0}\Na sucker for cuties, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Guinness World Record"\N"4-{\i1}Shaku Tama{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Konosu Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Today"\N"Minami Nanami: Aoi & I are on our way!"\N"Minami Nanami: Almost there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Today"\N"Minami Nanami: Aoi & I are on our way!"\N"Minami Nanami: Almost there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should pretend\Nwe've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard, fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And this here is Aoi--\Ncutie pie extraordinaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you! I'm Aoi Hinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm Hanabi Natsubayashi. Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so adorably tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I know this is sudden,\Nbut can I call you Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh-huh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and either Hinami or Aoi works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Um... Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're getting along great already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't their croquettes a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! But I, Minami Nanami,\Nhave a taste for grilled squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we split up\Nand buy both to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Hanabi? Want to try both?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm fine with just a croquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The grilled squid is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means it's up to you two\Nto pick up the croquettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go by myself. It's just croquettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is three enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Yummy!"\N"Grilled Squid"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hanabi's a tough one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? But that's what\Nmakes her so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, Mimimi. Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can tell, right?\NShe's a good, no-nonsense girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You, me, everyone--we can\Nbe better friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we make that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what got\Neveryone to warm up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started going by "Mimimi"--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that might've made it easier\Nto talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All like, "Mimimi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A nickname!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No crowds here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have you underestimating\Nmy research skills, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What beautiful {\i1}hanabi {\i0}fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but {\i1}this {\i0}Hanabi is the {\i1}cute {\i0}kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That was dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like {\i1}hanabi{\i0}, Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you're doing that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}love {\i0}Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a {\i1}different {\i0}Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hanabi!\N--Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard {\i1}that {\i0}old cheer in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna say it, Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're{\i1} hanabi{\i0}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You make no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess around with people's names!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tama, you're so strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "Tama" business?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a fireworks shell.\NYou're Hanabi, so: Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A great fit, right? Little {\i1}and {\i0}cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {\i1}I {\i0}think it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you blushing, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta... Tamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Tama's shouting "Tamaya"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}not {\i0}a firework!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Minmi is such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. See you, Minmi, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, that was a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, since you're involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd best not tell Hanabi\Nwe gave her that nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for her own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I'm {\i0}using it because I {\i1}like {\i0}it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mimimi. Always trying\Nto help out in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Fireworks"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty rich coming from {\i1}you{\i0}, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Trash: collected! Fire: extinguished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's hit it, Aoi--and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}were {\i0}just leaving, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--Tamaya!\N--Oh, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Saitama City"\N"City of Roses"\N"Chuo Ward"
